From 66f75ef98b7a800e782539c8c39b43ddbd37c6e0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 08:17:50 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Remove TermSurf app backend and OpenApp host path
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Drop gtui app descriptors, app-frontend registry, Deno backend spawn/
readiness, and OpenApp lifecycle handlers. Regenerate termsurf protobuf-c
stubs without OpenApp messages (tags 40–42 reserved in schema).
